data.description: This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Home located in Muscle Shoals is ready to call your forever home. Entering through the front, you will see a large living space that's perfect for TV watching, and family entertaining, with fireplace that has gas logs.  Schedule your viewing today to make this home your own, the possibilities are endless. This home is located minutes from schools, restaurants, and shopping.
